{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 62,
  "title": "第六十二章（為道）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "道者萬物之奧，"
    },
    {
      "text": "善人之寶，"
    },
    {
      "text": "不善人之所保。"
    },
    {
      "text": "美言可以市，"
    },
    {
      "text": "尊行可以加入。"
    },
    {
      "text": "人之不善，何棄之有。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故立天子，置三公，"
    },
    {
      "text": "雖有拱璧以先駟馬，不如坐進此道。"
    },
    {
      "text": "古之所以貴此道者，何不日以求得？"
    },
    {
      "text": "有罪以免耶，"
    },
    {
      "text": "故為天下貴。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "奧，藏也。道為萬物之藏，無所不容也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "善人以道為身寶，不敢違也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道者，不善人之保倚也。遭患逢急，猶知自悔卑下。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "美言者獨可於市耳。 夫市交易而退，不相宜善言美語，求者欲疾得，賣者欲疾售也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "加，別也。人有尊貴之行，可以別異於凡人，未足以尊道。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人雖不善，當以道化之。蓋三皇之前，無有棄民，德化淳也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "欲使教化不善之人。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 16
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "雖有美璧先駟馬而至，故不如坐進此道。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 16
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "古之所以貴此道者，不日日遠行求索，近得之於身。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "有罪謂遭亂世，闇君妄行形誅，修道則可以解死，免於眾也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道德洞遠，無不覆濟，全身治國，恬然無為，故可為天下貴也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
